#  Allows you to perform single operation 
#  on large set of s3 objects

Large Scale - Large set of s3 objects
Jobs are executed on the objects.

Use Cases
    - Copy or move large amount of data between s3 buckets
    or different storage classes

    - Change tags for large amounts of objects.

    - Combine with other AWS services to tranform data.

    - Encrypt large amount s3 objects.

#  S3 Select - Can use SQL like queries on CSVs and JSON
#  data in buckets.

example) select s.name from S3Object s where s.age > 25

# S3 event notifications
Can recieved notifications were certain events happen in
an S3 bucket.
    -New objects are created.
    -Objects are deleted.
    -Replication event
    -Restored objects
    -Lifecycle events
    -Object tagging event

Events can be sent to
    -SNS topics
    -SQS queues
    -AWS Lambda functions
    -Amazon EventBridge buses

Use Cases
    -Image is uploaded to S3 bucket and lambda function
    is triggered that resizes it and pushes it to another
    bucket.
    -Compliance - Object is uploaded and a workflow is
    triggered to analyze the object to confirm that the
    data uploaded isn't sensitive.